@startuml
title AD-02: Dashboard Asset View and Listing (Swimlane Diagram)

|User|
start

|System|
:Determine user role;
:Load role-specific dashboard;
:Retrieve initial asset list;
:Display asset table;

|User|
:Scroll asset table;

|System|
if (more assets available?) then (yes)
    |User|
    :Select Show More Assets;
    
    |System|
    :Retrieve additional assets;
    :Append assets to table;
    :Update dashboard view;
    
    --> User
else (no)
endif

|User|
:Select / interact with assets (view details, reserve, download documents, etc);

stop
@enduml
